收皮啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"多謝支持！"},{"pid":"bfbb97fab7f76dcd9f3a373debb204bb4a7a64db","tid":1435324,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"Btw 之前D片都可以睇架😂"},{"pid":"2d895a5c178b2630fac6430722d5edcb9645d521","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc580da6732a7182317aa8ca3de615279ceb27a","tid":1435324,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙普選設時限，為港獨正名，不能無了期五大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434739</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"dd3ddec30eb81a35028d42cd06e862c522c6c0cb","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f6db46cae6073c723d68392b4cf6f17ece5749","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1325e56d717d80053f1d7831ab6b8afd6f2fbbac","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88185c4ca4bfe73386fb0405933f2f6a049b708b","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b4bc5c6193110761979791a3a2ce8af86fc016","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8bd67e7cae64e14fb5e21ac0c2c524a552f577","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef080af36e93805d6b94a0c6b2e86ab84ed00af4","tid":1435324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime